core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇咩特別想做，只想係平平凡凡咁過，之後係訓訓下覺咁就死左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會後悔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又冇咩特別想要<br />\n而且都得返三個月就唔搞咁多野<br />\n一陣做到天一半地一半就唔好啦<br />\n做返自己算啦</blockquote><br />\n你既睇法都岩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c46e7883d2142e838677f2f873adb34318d9e99","tid":146221,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"同佢講「今生我地做唔到情侶，下世我一定會搵到你，繼續愛你。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead0409780ca4fa2474f8ae24304cb249f4c39e4","tid":146221,"uid":7363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開心<br />\n可以唔洗捱貴租，睇人面色做人，離開呢個全部野都扭曲左既世界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個世界真係愈黎愈不撚知所謂<br />\n<br />\n日日返工都唔知為乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5d29f17c6bbdbdd7339847097a2d4c7d68eff5","tid":146221,"uid":46588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>約哂所有朋友出黎玩一個月先<br />\n遊哂全香港同埋食哂所有好味既野<br />\n但夜晚要番屋企食飯傾偈<br />\n同屋企人講下去左邊玩食左d咩<br />\n第二個月就搭飛機去追下星先<br />\n追夠就喺屋企過埋最後嗰個月<br />\n同屋企人又係咩都做下氹佢地開心<br />\n跟住最尾嗰日先同大家講我就走啦<br />\n咁就可以一早講定想同我講既野<br />\n然後就冇乜遺憾咁帶住好多開心回憶咁走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好似好浪漫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇到好後悔 點解唔陪多d屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對唔住啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72964f356205225447836a873767e3c744d89f1","tid":146221,"uid":7363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"有冇睇100毛<br />\n<br />\n如果你有5年命<br />\n<br />\n係咪睇左你個post啊師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe66722e5ae11cece7cd463b6a6e74b86e05f75d","tid":146221,"uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"反正唔會延長自己既有生之年，點解唔試試縮短其他人既有生之年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14cd806fe38ec2516f93e72540c26a40953631e","tid":146221,"uid":72279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"去曬三個月旅行 然後靜靜雞消失 <br />\n死前去過既每個地方都寄明信片比朋友同家人<br />\n死後就會收到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68e16fd238a487ac572f02b6cd32320c1654d60","tid":146221,"uid":601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇睇100毛<br />\n<br />\n如果你有5年命<br />\n<br />\n係咪睇左你個post啊師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8806790dd1464987592d3fc262152b68c38283","tid":146221,"uid":601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去曬三個月旅行 然後靜靜雞消失 <br /